  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Candy & Toys Store Simulator! </strong><br><br><strong>Candy & Toys Store Simulator </strong>is a business simulation where you run and grow your own candy and toy store in a calm, cozy, and lively environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handle daily operations such as stocking shelves, setting prices, serving customers, and organizing your store to maximize efficiency and profit. As you progress, you can hire employees and unlock new opportunities to expand and improve your store operations. <br>‚Äé‚Äé <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/657497c6ae909237c6c3c2a6bbd70f96.webp?t=1774380685\" width=800 height=4 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Store Layout & Design:</strong> <br>Optimize the layout of your candy and toys store for efficiency and visual appeal. Design your space to maximize usability, organize aisles strategically, place products wisely, and create a smooth, enjoyable shopping experience for your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/0b0d86550a972c66d153cc59be8190a6.poster.avif?t=1774380685\" width=618 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/0b0d86550a972c66d153cc59be8190a6.webm?t=1774380685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/0b0d86550a972c66d153cc59be8190a6.mp4?t=1774380685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‚Äé‚Äé‚Äé</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/657497c6ae909237c6c3c2a6bbd70f96.webp?t=1774380685\" width=800 height=4 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock and own a Gaming Club:</strong> <br>Progress through the game to unlock and purchase a Gaming Club, giving you a new space to manage, customize, and generate additional income alongside your store.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/7a43bd44b5cf0bb0d365299be405f0fb.poster.avif?t=1774380685\" width=618 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/7a43bd44b5cf0bb0d365299be405f0fb.webm?t=1774380685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/7a43bd44b5cf0bb0d365299be405f0fb.mp4?t=1774380685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/657497c6ae909237c6c3c2a6bbd70f96.webp?t=1774380685\" width=800 height=4 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manage Inventory & Pricing:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take full control of your store‚Äôs stock and prices. Keep shelves filled, adjust pricing for maximum profit, and ensure your customers always find what they need.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/03896dbdf0ca8f9847ff7db5ae70ecad.poster.avif?t=1774380685\" width=618 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/03896dbdf0ca8f9847ff7db5ae70ecad.webm?t=1774380685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/03896dbdf0ca8f9847ff7db5ae70ecad.mp4?t=1774380685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‚Äé</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/657497c6ae909237c6c3c2a6bbd70f96.webp?t=1774380685\" width=800 height=4 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade and Customize Both Locations:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your store and Gaming Club to reflect your style. Expand your store, change wall and floor colors in both locations, and add your personal logo to the Gaming Club.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/9107352fcbfaf11655fa3014c55f6dec.poster.avif?t=1774380685\" width=618 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/9107352fcbfaf11655fa3014c55f6dec.webm?t=1774380685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013700/extras/9107352fcbfaf11655fa3014c55f6dec.mp4?t=1774380685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong> <br>‚Äé</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‚Äé‚Äé‚Äé‚Äé <br>Enjoy running your store and Gaming Club at your own pace. Decorate, upgrade, and watch your business grow while having fun managing every detail. <br><br><strong>Have Fun!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‚Äé‚Äé</p></li></ul>",
